com.gl.vn.me.ko.pies.platform.client.tcp

Interface TcpChannelInitializer

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface TcpChannelInitializer
    Performs initialization of new SocketChannels created by TcpSequentialClient.

    This interface is similar to ChannelInitializer class except it doesn't implement ChannelHandler and the method initChannel(SocketChannel) is accessible from TcpSequentialClient.

    • Method Summary

      void initChannel(SocketChannel channel)
      This method will be called once the Channel was registered.
